cription\":\"IP地址池的起始IP地址。（例如：192.168.0.251）\",\"label\":\"IP地址池结束值\",\"default\":\"192.168.0.251\",\"constraints\":[{\"allowed_pattern\":\"^(1\\\\d{2}|2[0-4]\\\\d|25[0-5]|[1-9]\\\\d|[1-9])\\\\.(((1\\\\d{2}|2[0-4]\\\\d|25[0-5]|[1-9]\\\\d|\\\\d)\\\\.){2})(1\\\\d{2}|2[0-4]\\\\d|25[0-5]|[1-9]\\\\d|\\\\d)$\",\"description\":\"IP地址格式：(1~255).(0~255).(0~255).(0~255)。\"}],\"type\":\"string\"}},\"metadata\":{\"Designer\":{\"33e33304-eb2a-4ab1-903c-9c95f4ac24e8\":{\"size\":{\"width\":120,\"height\":120},\"position\":{\"x\":570,\"y\":190},\"z\":1,\"embeds\":[\"e78cc29e-35df-49a1-b4a4-c803ad5e774d\"]},\"e78cc29e-35df-49a1-b4a4-c803ad5e774d\":{\"size\":{\"width\":72,\"height\":72},\"position\":{\"x\":600,\"y\":220},\"z\":2,\"parent\":\"33e33304-eb2a-4ab1-903c-9c95f4ac24e8\"},\"b889b79e-e48f-4f36-8c45-8f67d3c914da\":{\"size\":{\"width\":72,\"height\":72},\"position\":{\"x\":440,\"y\":220},\"z\":1,\"embeds\":[],\"isassociatedwith\":[\"e78cc29e-35df-49a1-b4a4-c803ad5e774d\",\"130df212-9d31-401b-b91b-1ed7e0593bee\"]},\"130df212-9d31-401b-b91b-1ed7e0593bee\":{\"size\":{\"width\":72,\"height\":72},\"position\":{\"x\":290,\"y\":220},\"z\":1},\"6af581bb-93b4-41a2-84e9-8493c7665b83\":{\"source\":{\"id\":\"b889b79e-e48f-4f36-8c45-8f67d3c914da\"},\"target\":{\"id\":\"e78cc29e-35df-49a1-b4a4-c803ad5e774d\"},\"z\":2},\"49c6b478-0a05-4397-92b5-a337e1fecd9d\":{\"source\":{\"id\":\"b889b79e-e48f-4f36-8c45-8f67d3c914da\"},\"target\":{\"id\":\"130df212-9d31-401b-b91b-1ed7e0593bee\"},\"z\":1}},\"relationships\":{\"e78cc29e-35df-49a1-b4a4-c803ad5e774d\":{\"references\":{\"network\":{\"get_resource\":\"net\"}}},\"5825db98-2905-4794-81d7-9ca60a08d082\":{\"references\":{\"parent\":{}}},\"1e205db0-de87-4653-a604-49e96a611b34\":{\"references\":{\"router\":[],\"subnet\":{}}},\"130df212-9d31-401b-b91b-1ed7e0593bee\":{\"references\":{\"parent\":{\"get_resource\":\"routerinterface\"}}},\"b889b79e-e48f-4f36-8c45-8f67d3c914da\":{\"references\":{\"router\":{\"get_resource\":\"router\"},\"subnet\":{\"get_resou
